{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.1","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:1","prev_osis_id":"Matt.009.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-15: cf. (Mc 3:13-19; 6:7-11. Lu 6:12-16; 9:1-5.) Lu 10:1-12. Ac 1:13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Puis, ayant appel\u00e9 ses douze disciples, il leur donna le pouvoir de chasser les esprits impurs, et de gu\u00e9rir toute maladie et toute infirmit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.2","name":"Matthieu 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.9.38","name":"Matthieu 9:38","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.9.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.2","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:2","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Voici les noms des douze ap\u00f4tres. Le premier, Simon appel\u00e9 Pierre, et Andr\u00e9, son fr\u00e8re; Jacques, fils de Z\u00e9b\u00e9d\u00e9e, et Jean, son fr\u00e8re;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.3","name":"Matthieu 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.1","name":"Matthieu 10:1","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.3","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:3","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Philippe, et Barth\u00e9lemy; Thomas, et Matthieu, le publicain; Jacques, fils d\u2019Alph\u00e9e, et Thadd\u00e9e;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.4","name":"Matthieu 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.2","name":"Matthieu 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.4","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:4","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Simon le Cananite, et Judas l\u2019Iscariot, celui qui livra J\u00e9sus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.5","name":"Matthieu 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.3","name":"Matthieu 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.5","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:5","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Tels sont les douze que J\u00e9sus envoya, apr\u00e8s leur avoir donn\u00e9 les instructions suivantes: <span class=\"wj\">N\u2019allez pas vers les pa\u00efens, et n\u2019entrez pas dans les villes des Samaritains;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.6","name":"Matthieu 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.4","name":"Matthieu 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.6","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:6","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">allez plut\u00f4t vers les brebis perdues de la maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.7","name":"Matthieu 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.5","name":"Matthieu 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.7","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:7","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Allez,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">pr\u00eachez, et dites: Le royaume des cieux est proche.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.8","name":"Matthieu 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.6","name":"Matthieu 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.8","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:8","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Gu\u00e9rissez les malades, ressuscitez les morts, purifiez les l\u00e9preux, chassez les d\u00e9mons.<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Vous avez re\u00e7u gratuitement, donnez gratuitement.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.9","name":"Matthieu 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.7","name":"Matthieu 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.9","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:9","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ne prenez ni or, ni argent, ni monnaie, dans vos ceintures;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.10","name":"Matthieu 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.8","name":"Matthieu 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.10","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:10","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">ni sac pour le voyage, ni deux tuniques, ni souliers, ni b\u00e2ton;<\/span><span class=\"wj\">car l\u2019ouvrier m\u00e9rite sa nourriture.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.11","name":"Matthieu 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.9","name":"Matthieu 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.11","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:11","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Dans quelque ville ou village que vous entriez, informez-vous s\u2019il s\u2019y trouve quelque homme digne de vous recevoir; et demeurez chez lui jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que vous partiez.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.12","name":"Matthieu 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.10","name":"Matthieu 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.12","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:12","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">En entrant dans la maison, saluez-la;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.13","name":"Matthieu 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.11","name":"Matthieu 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.13","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:13","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">et, si la maison en est digne, que votre paix vienne sur elle; mais si elle n\u2019en est pas digne, que votre paix retourne \u00e0 vous.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.14","name":"Matthieu 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.12","name":"Matthieu 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.14","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:14","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Lorsqu\u2019on ne vous recevra pas et qu\u2019on n\u2019\u00e9coutera pas vos paroles, sortez de cette maison ou de cette ville et<\/span><span class=\"wj\">secouez la poussi\u00e8re de vos pieds.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.15","name":"Matthieu 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.13","name":"Matthieu 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.15","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:15","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9: au jour du jugement, le pays de Sodome et de Gomorrhe sera trait\u00e9 moins rigoureusement que cette ville-l\u00e0.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.16","name":"Matthieu 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.14","name":"Matthieu 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.16","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:16","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.017,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 16-39: cf. Lu 12:4-12, 51-53; 14:26-33; 21:12-17.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Voici, je vous envoie comme des brebis au milieu des loups. Soyez donc prudents comme les serpents, et simples comme les colombes.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.17","name":"Matthieu 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.15","name":"Matthieu 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.17","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:17","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mettez-vous en garde contre les hommes;<\/span><span class=\"wj\">car ils vous livreront aux tribunaux, et ils vous battront de verges dans leurs synagogues;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.18","name":"Matthieu 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.16","name":"Matthieu 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.18","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:18","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">vous serez men\u00e9s, \u00e0 cause de moi, devant des gouverneurs et devant des rois, pour servir de t\u00e9moignage \u00e0 eux et aux pa\u00efens.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.19","name":"Matthieu 10:19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.17","name":"Matthieu 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.19","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:19","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais, quand on vous livrera, ne vous inqui\u00e9tez ni de la mani\u00e8re dont vous parlerez ni de ce que vous direz: ce que vous aurez \u00e0 dire vous sera donn\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019heure m\u00eame;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.20","name":"Matthieu 10:20","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.18","name":"Matthieu 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.20","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:20","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">car ce n\u2019est pas vous qui parlerez, c\u2019est l\u2019Esprit de votre P\u00e8re qui parlera en vous.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.21","name":"Matthieu 10:21","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.19","name":"Matthieu 10:19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.21","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:21","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Le fr\u00e8re livrera son fr\u00e8re \u00e0 la mort, et le p\u00e8re son enfant; les enfants se soul\u00e8veront contre leurs parents, et les feront mourir.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.22","name":"Matthieu 10:22","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.20","name":"Matthieu 10:20","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.22","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:22","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Vous serez ha\u00efs de tous, \u00e0 cause de mon nom;<\/span><span class=\"wj\">mais celui qui pers\u00e9v\u00e9rera jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la fin sera sauv\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.23","name":"Matthieu 10:23","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.21","name":"Matthieu 10:21","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.23","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:23","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Quand on vous pers\u00e9cutera dans une ville, fuyez dans une autre. Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9, vous n\u2019aurez pas achev\u00e9 de parcourir les villes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl que le Fils de l\u2019homme sera venu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.24","name":"Matthieu 10:24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.22","name":"Matthieu 10:22","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.24","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:24","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Le disciple n\u2019est pas plus que le ma\u00eetre, ni le serviteur plus que son seigneur.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.25","name":"Matthieu 10:25","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.23","name":"Matthieu 10:23","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.25","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:25","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il suffit au disciple d\u2019\u00eatre trait\u00e9 comme son ma\u00eetre, et au serviteur comme son seigneur.<\/span><span class=\"wj\">S\u2019ils ont appel\u00e9 le ma\u00eetre de la maison B\u00e9elz\u00e9bul, \u00e0 combien plus forte raison appelleront-ils ainsi les gens de sa maison!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.26","name":"Matthieu 10:26","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.24","name":"Matthieu 10:24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.26","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:26","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ne les craignez donc point;<\/span><span class=\"wj\">car il n\u2019y a rien de cach\u00e9 qui ne doive \u00eatre d\u00e9couvert, ni de secret qui ne doive \u00eatre connu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.27","name":"Matthieu 10:27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.25","name":"Matthieu 10:25","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.27","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:27","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ce que je vous dis dans les t\u00e9n\u00e8bres, dites-le en plein jour; et ce qui vous est dit \u00e0 l\u2019oreille, pr\u00eachez-le sur les toits.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.28","name":"Matthieu 10:28","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.26","name":"Matthieu 10:26","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.28","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:28","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ne craignez pas ceux qui tuent le corps et qui ne peuvent tuer l\u2019\u00e2me; craignez plut\u00f4t celui qui peut faire p\u00e9rir l\u2019\u00e2me et le corps dans la g\u00e9henne.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.29","name":"Matthieu 10:29","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.27","name":"Matthieu 10:27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.29","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:29","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ne vend-on pas deux passereaux pour un sou? Cependant, il n\u2019en tombe pas un \u00e0 terre sans la volont\u00e9 de votre P\u00e8re.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.30","name":"Matthieu 10:30","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.28","name":"Matthieu 10:28","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.30","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:30","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et m\u00eame les<\/span><span class=\"wj\">cheveux de votre t\u00eate sont tous compt\u00e9s.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.31","name":"Matthieu 10:31","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.29","name":"Matthieu 10:29","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.31","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:31","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ne craignez donc point: vous valez plus que beaucoup de passereaux.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.32","name":"Matthieu 10:32","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.30","name":"Matthieu 10:30","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.32","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:32","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">C\u2019est pourquoi, quiconque me confessera devant les hommes, je le confesserai aussi devant mon P\u00e8re qui est dans les cieux;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.33","name":"Matthieu 10:33","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.31","name":"Matthieu 10:31","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.33","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:33","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">mais quiconque me reniera devant les hommes, je le renierai aussi devant mon P\u00e8re qui est dans les cieux.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.34","name":"Matthieu 10:34","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.32","name":"Matthieu 10:32","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.34","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:34","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ne croyez pas que je sois venu apporter la paix sur la terre; je ne suis pas venu apporter la paix, mais l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.35","name":"Matthieu 10:35","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.33","name":"Matthieu 10:33","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.35","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:35","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car je suis venu mettre la division entre l\u2019homme et son p\u00e8re, entre la fille et sa m\u00e8re, entre la belle-fille et sa belle-m\u00e8re;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.36","name":"Matthieu 10:36","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.34","name":"Matthieu 10:34","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.36","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:36","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">et l\u2019homme aura pour ennemis les gens de sa maison.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.37","name":"Matthieu 10:37","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.35","name":"Matthieu 10:35","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.37","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:37","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Celui qui aime son p\u00e8re ou sa m\u00e8re plus que moi n\u2019est pas digne de moi, et celui qui aime son fils ou sa fille plus que moi n\u2019est pas digne de moi;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.38","name":"Matthieu 10:38","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.36","name":"Matthieu 10:36","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.38","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:38","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">celui qui ne prend pas sa croix, et ne me suit pas, n\u2019est pas digne de moi.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.39","name":"Matthieu 10:39","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.37","name":"Matthieu 10:37","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.39","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:39","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Celui qui conservera sa vie la perdra, et celui qui perdra sa vie \u00e0 cause de moi la retrouvera.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.40","name":"Matthieu 10:40","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.38","name":"Matthieu 10:38","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.40","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:40","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.041,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">10 v. 40 \u00e0 11 v. 1: cf. Mt 25:34-40.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Celui qui vous re\u00e7oit me re\u00e7oit, et celui qui me re\u00e7oit, re\u00e7oit celui qui m\u2019a envoy\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.41","name":"Matthieu 10:41","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.39","name":"Matthieu 10:39","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.41","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:41","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.010.042,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Celui qui re\u00e7oit un proph\u00e8te en qualit\u00e9 de proph\u00e8te recevra une r\u00e9compense de proph\u00e8te, et celui qui re\u00e7oit un juste en qualit\u00e9 de juste recevra une r\u00e9compense de juste.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.42","name":"Matthieu 10:42","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.40","name":"Matthieu 10:40","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.42","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 10:42","prev_osis_id":"Matt.010.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.011.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.10.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et quiconque donnera seulement un verre d\u2019eau froide \u00e0 l\u2019un de ces petits parce qu\u2019il est mon disciple, je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9, il ne perdra point sa r\u00e9compense.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.10","name":"Matthieu 10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.11.1","name":"Matthieu 11:1","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.11.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.10.41","name":"Matthieu 10:41","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.10.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb6ce2f89.72234304');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb6ce2f89.72234304\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb6ce2f89.72234304","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb6ce2f89.72234304'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb6ce2f89.72234304\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}